column5: Heading there next weekend for 5 days with our boys anyone have any info they can share? Im told we will get lots of smallies/pike which is fine however we will be hoping for Eyes,dont have to be big ones just eaters is fine will be staying at a lodge at south end and know this lake is 40 miles long but in a 14 footer with a 9.9 hp doubt we will be heading too far up it
